# Python backend (deltai)

- After substantive changes under `project/`, run verification from `project/` with the venv active:
  - `python tests/verify_full.py`
  - `python tests/verify_stress.py` and `python tests/verify_resource_mgmt.py` when routing, tools, or resource code changes
  - `python tests/verify_distill.py` when training/distillation code changes
- Do not commit `project/.env`, secrets, or generated data under `data/`. Follow `.gitignore`.
